OL,3,C'Can we please live in peace
OL,4,Ctogether?' asks Belfast resident after
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,FThere has been widespread condemnation
OL,8,Fof Tuesday night's scenes of disorder
OL,9,Ffollowing a shocking knife attack in
OL,10,FBelfast.
OL,12,FThere were a number of protests around
OL,13,FNorthern Ireland in the wake of the
OL,14,Fattack. While some passed off
OL,15,Fpeacefully, violence did flare in
OL,16,Fpockets.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/11
