OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1781277116
OL,3,C'Can we please live in peace
OL,4,Ctogether?' asks Belfast resident after
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,FMultiple rioters set homes, a bus and
OL,8,Fcars on fire, with people targeted
OL,9,Fbased on their race.
OL,11,FIt followed the attack on Stephen
OL,12,FOgilvy in the Kinnaird Avenue area of
OL,13,Fnorth Belfast on Monday.
OL,15,FA court heard the victim has lost his
OL,16,Fleft eye and has severe damage to his
OL,17,Fright eye, as well as deep cuts to his
OL,18,Fhead and face, and long lacerations on
OL,19,Fhis back.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/11
