OL,3,C'Can we please live in peace
OL,4,Ctogether?' asks Belfast resident after
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,FHis family appealed for privacy, but
OL,8,Furged people not to use the attack to
OL,9,F"divide people or fuel hostility".
OL,11,F'I'm so scared'
OL,13,FMultiple individuals and families were
OL,14,Fforced to flee from their homes.
OL,16,FMany of the those targeted were
OL,17,Fforeign nationals, leaving many
OL,18,Fcommunities living in fear.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/11
