OL,3,C'Can we please live in peace
OL,4,Ctogether?' asks Belfast resident after
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,FA resident in east Belfast, Anselme
OL,8,FShima asked: "Can we please live in
OL,9,Fpeace together?"
OL,11,FTwo care workers were terrified to
OL,12,Fleave their home after being attacked
OL,13,Fby masked youths.
OL,15,FStella Ariokot said: "Right now I'm so
OL,16,Fscared. I can't go back to the house.
OL,17,FIt was really so terrifying."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/11
