OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1781277116
OL,3,C'Can we please live in peace
OL,4,Ctogether?' asks Belfast resident after
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,FHadi Alodid appeared before Belfast's
OL,8,FMagistrates' Court over the violent
OL,9,Fattack which sparked the wave of
OL,10,Fprotests and disorder.
OL,12,FThe 30-year-old, with an address at
OL,13,FDuncairn Avenue in Belfast, is charged
OL,14,Fwith the attempted murder of Stephen
OL,15,FOgilvy, threatening to kill an NHS
OL,16,Fradiographer on the same day and with
OL,17,Fpossession of a knife.
OL,19,FHe appeared in court via videolink.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
