OL,3,C'Can we please live in peace
OL,4,Ctogether?' asks Belfast resident after
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,FHe refused legal representation, made
OL,8,Fno reply to charges and was refused
OL,9,Fbail.
OL,11,FAlodid is next due to appear in court
OL,12,Fin four weeks' time.
OL,14,FViolence 'shocking and completely
OL,15,Funacceptable'
OL,17,FThere has been widespread disruption
OL,18,Fwith notice of planned protests on
OL,19,FWednesday forcing businesses and
OL,20,Fschools to close.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/11
