OL,3,C'Can we please live in peace
OL,4,Ctogether?' asks Belfast resident after
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,FPoliticians and journalists have been
OL,8,Fthreatened. The Lord Mayor of Belfast
OL,9,Fsaid she has received death threats,
OL,10,Fsaying they "will not deter" her from
OL,11,Fher work.
OL,13,FTwo police officers were injured on
OL,14,FTuesday.
OL,16,FThree arrests were made and two people
OL,17,Fso far have been charged over the
OL,18,Fdisorder.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/11
