OL,3,C'Can we please live in peace
OL,4,Ctogether?' asks Belfast resident after
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,FThe Prime Minister said the disorder
OL,8,Fin Belfast was "shocking and
OL,9,Fcompletely unacceptable", adding: "It
OL,10,Fis clear that people were targeted
OL,11,Flast night because of their background
OL,12,Fand I will not tolerate it."
OL,14,FSir Keir Starmer has vowed to "crack
OL,15,Fdown on anyone who is fuelling this
OL,16,Fdivision".
