OL,3,C'Can we please live in peace
OL,4,Ctogether?' asks Belfast resident after
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,FPSNI Chief Constable Jon Boutcher
OL,8,Fdescribed the violence as "an act of
OL,9,Fself harm" and an "insult" to the
OL,10,Fbrave actions of those that sought to
OL,11,Fhelp the victim in knife attack.
OL,13,FHe said police would be on the streets
OL,14,Fin greater numbers and appealed for
OL,15,Fcalm.
